 construire ont une moyenne de taux d\u2019\u00e9nergies renouvelables de 73\u00a0%, des coefficients de biotope entre 41 et 75\u00a0% et des coefficients de pleine terre entre 38 et 67\u00a0%.<\/span><\/p>\n","ajouter_une_image_a_droite_action":true,"visuel_action":{"ID":4216,"id":4216,"title":"\u00c9coquartier de la carri\u00e8re des Granges","filename":"Ecoquartier-des-Granges-phase-amenagement-@Drone-Rhone-Alpes.jpg","filesize":579813,"url":"https:\/\/territoireengagetransitionecologique.ademe.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Ecoquartier-des-Granges-phase-amenagement-@Drone-Rhone-Alpes.jpg","link":"https:\/\/territoireengagetransitionecologique.ademe.fr\/collectivites\/la-motte-servolex\/dcim102mediadji_0182-jpg\/","alt":"\u00c9coquartier de la carri\u00e8re des Granges","author":"8","description":"","caption":"\u00c9coquartier de la carri\u00e8re des Granges","name":"dcim102mediadji_0182-jpg","status":"inherit","uploaded_to":4203,"date":"2022-03-22 13:21:53","modified":"2022-03-22 13:22:46","menu_order":0,"mime_type":"image\/jpeg","type":"image","subtype":"jpeg","icon":"https:\/\/territoireengagetransitionecologique.ademe.fr\/wp-includes\/images\/media\/default.png","width":2000,"height":1500,"sizes":{"thumbnail":"https:\/\/territoireengagetransitionecologique.ademe.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Ecoquartier-des-Granges-phase-amenagement-@Drone-Rhone-Alpes-150x150.jpg","thumbnail-width":150,"thumbnail-height":150,"medium":"https:\/\/territoireengagetransitionecologique.ademe.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Ecoquartier-des-Granges-phase-amenagement-@Drone-Rhone-Alpes-250x188.jpg","medium-width":250,"medium-height":188,"medium_large":"https:\/\/territoireengagetransitionecologique.ademe.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Ecoquartier-des-Granges-phase-amenagement-@Drone-Rhone-Alpes-768x576.jpg","medium_large-width":768,"medium_large-height":576,"large":"https:\/\/territoireengagetransitionecologique.ademe.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/Ecoquartier-des